WEBVTT

00:06:27.548 --> 00:06:31.691
And now, we've shared that language
with journalists, to adopt this.

00:06:31.715 --> 00:06:33.771
We've shared that language with activists.

00:06:33.795 --> 00:06:36.636
We're advising the National Emergency
Number Association,

00:06:36.660 --> 00:06:38.557
the 911 Association,

00:06:38.581 --> 00:06:42.151
on best practices
for first responders in suicide.

00:06:42.175 --> 00:06:44.540
And we're working
with the Veterans Administration

00:06:44.564 --> 00:06:47.635
to identify suicidal ideation
and intent in veterans.

00:06:48.016 --> 00:06:50.358
(Sighs)

00:06:50.382 --> 00:06:52.482
Pain isn't an American experience.

00:06:52.506 --> 00:06:54.379
It's a human experience.

00:06:54.403 --> 00:06:56.807
So we've been growing.

00:06:56.831 --> 00:07:00.490
So far, we've been expanding
one country at a time: